  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Irresponsible and tactless actions have led to disaster - Sri Lankan Tamil Republic Party",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "When we are a party with 70 years of experience, tactless and irresponsible arbitrary actions are causing disaster, said Mawai Senathiraja, president of the Sri Lankan Tamil Republic Party.",
        "He said this while commenting on the current situation to the media.",
        "A written agreement is said to have been reached with Dallas Alagapperuma and Sajith Premadasa, who were present when the TNA parliamentary meeting took place.",
        "I couldn't go to that event. This issue has been reported to the media overnight.",
        "At the time when the presidential election was going on, the members of parliament were divided into two and the situation was revealed at night that Dallas Alhakaperuma and Sajith Premadasa had reached an agreement with the Tamil National Federation.",
        "This is a serious situation. If such an agreement had been reached, it could have been published after winning.",
        "It is enough for parliamentarians and people's representatives to know that. In the meantime, it is not acceptable to say it out loud. Due to this, unexpected election results may occur.",
        "It has been reported that among the parliamentarians of the Tamil National Federation, there is an opinion that the decision against Ranil should be taken only by forcing India. I don't know its truth.",
        "Whatever it is, I strongly condemn the decision to utter India's name. It is a non-diplomatic non-strategic issue and creates a problem. Many people are fighting with me because of such news.",
        "After this news was published, the next morning, there was a news in the media in the name of Sumanthran that he had not signed any such document and had not accepted it.",
        "All these are reckless actions without tactics. Due to this, Dulles Alagapuruma could not get the expected votes and Ranil got 134 votes as expected.",
        "When you are a party with 70 years of experience, how much disaster has been caused by such arbitrary actions.",
        "I am very worried about the possibility of having to drag India to say that we do not believe in our opinion.",
        "It is serious if the decision to vote for the Dulles beauty is based on such behavior.",
        "This opinion is very negative. It is a very wrong message to mention the name of India which is our absolute strength. He said that massive consequences will have to be faced."
      ],
